pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `daily_inspection` ( `check_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `eq_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `clearing_check` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `physical_check` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `function_check` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `power_check` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `clearing_problem` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `physical_problem` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `function_problem` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `power_problem` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `check_date` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`check_no`), KEY `eq_no` (`eq_no`), CONSTRAINT `daily_inspection_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`eq_no`) REFERENCES `equipement` (`eq_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `engineer` ( `eng_fname` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_mname` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_lname` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `eng_country` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_city` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_address` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eng_salary` int(11) NOT NULL, `eng_hours` int(11) NOT NULL, `dep_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `eng_birthdate` date DEFAULT NULL, `ssd` int(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`eng_no`), UNIQUE KEY `SSd` (`ssd`), KEY `dep_no` (`dep_no`), KEY `ssd_2` (`ssd`), CONSTRAINT `engineer_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`dep_no`) REFERENCES `dep` (`dep_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=10 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `equipement` ( `eq_name` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `eq_make` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `eq_model` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `eq_country` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eq_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `eq_code` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `eq_serial` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eq_entry_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `eq_start_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `eq_waranty_period` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `eq_supplier_no` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `eq_price` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `ep_service_sup_no` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `eq_service_kind` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `eq_service_start` date DEFAULT NULL, `eq_service_end` date DEFAULT NULL, `dep_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `eq_room_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `parts` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`eq_no`), KEY `ep_service_sup_no` (`ep_service_sup_no`), KEY `eq_supplier_no` (`eq_supplier_no`), KEY `eq_room_equipement_no` (`eq_room_no`), CONSTRAINT `eq_room_equipement_no` FOREIGN KEY (`eq_room_no`) REFERENCES `room` (`room_no`), CONSTRAINT `equipement_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`ep_service_sup_no`) REFERENCES `service_supplier` (`sup_no`), CONSTRAINT `equipement_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`eq_supplier_no`) REFERENCES `supplier` (`sup_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `ppm` ( `check_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `eq_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `check_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `eng_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `t_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `battery_fault` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `circuit_fault` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `cable_fault` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `software_fault` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `wrong_output` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `wrong_output_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `software_fault_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `internal_malfunction` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `internal_malfunction_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `incorrect_connection` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `incorrect_connection_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `current_leak` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `physical_leak` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `part_not_functionning` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `part_not_functionning_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `continous_alarm` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `no_alarm` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `change_part` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `change_part_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `cost` int(11) NOT NULL, `battery_fault_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `circuit_fault_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `cable_fault_details` varchar(500) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `continous_alarm_details` varchar(500) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `no_alarm_details` varchar(500) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`check_no`), KEY `eng_no` (`eng_no`), KEY `t_no` (`t_no`), CONSTRAINT `ppm_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`eng_no`) REFERENCES `engineer` (`eng_no`), CONSTRAINT `ppm_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`t_no`) REFERENCES `technician` (`t_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=93 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `purchase` ( `p_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `p_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `p_expect_date` date DEFAULT NULL, `p_status` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `p_sup_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `p_product` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `p_unit_no` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `p_unit_cost` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `p_additional_cost` int(11) DEFAULT NULL, `p_additional_cost_details` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `p_eng_no` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`p_no`), KEY `p_sup_no` (`p_sup_no`), KEY `p_eng_no` (`p_eng_no`), CONSTRAINT `purchase_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`p_sup_no`) REFERENCES `supplier` (`sup_no`), CONSTRAINT `purchase_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`p_eng_no`) REFERENCES `engineer` (`eng_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `room` ( `room_name` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `room_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `dep_no` int(11) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`room_no`), KEY `dep_no` (`dep_no`), CONSTRAINT `room_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`dep_no`) REFERENCES `dep` (`dep_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=85 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `service_supplier` ( `sup_name` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `sup_country` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_city` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_address` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, PRIMARY KEY (`sup_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=13 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `service_sup_contact` ( `sup_contact` varchar(250) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `sup_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `contact_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, UNIQUE KEY `UNIQUE` (`contact_no`), KEY `sup_no` (`sup_no`), CONSTRAINT `service_sup_contact_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`sup_no`) REFERENCES `service_supplier` (`sup_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `supplier` ( `sup_name` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `sup_country` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_city` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `sup_address` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`sup_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=19 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `sup_contact` ( `sup_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `sup_contact` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `contact_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, UNIQUE KEY `UNIQUE` (`contact_no`), KEY `sup_no` (`sup_no`), CONSTRAINT `sup_contact_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`sup_no`) REFERENCES `supplier` (`sup_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;

CREATE TABLE `technician` ( `t_fname` varchar(255) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `t_mname` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci NOT NULL, `t_lname` varchar(250) CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci NOT NULL, `t_no` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `t_country` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `t_city` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `t_address` varchar(255) COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci DEFAULT NULL, `t_salary` int(11) NOT NULL, `t_hours` int(11) NOT NULL, `dep_no` int(11) NOT NULL, `t_birthdate` date DEFAULT NULL, `ssd` int(20) NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`t_no`), UNIQUE KEY `ssd` (`ssd`), KEY `dep_no` (`dep_no`), CONSTRAINT `technician_ibfk_1` FOREIGN KEY (`dep_no`) REFERENCES `dep` (`dep_no`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=2 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_general_ci;
